<LP>
   RICHMOND, Va. -- Heilig-Meyers Co. reported that April
sales rose 7.6%, to $32.2 million, from $29.9 million a year
ago.
   The home furnishings retailer said same-store sales rose
1%. The company currently operates 306 stores in 12 states.
